  "description": "A long-distance shot of the Golden Gate Bridge spanning a vast body of water, likely the San Francisco Bay. The bridge is a vibrant orange-red against the backdrop of a hazy blue sky and sea. In the foreground, branches with green and reddish leaves partially frame the view, creating a natural border. To the left of the bridge, a small island with a building is visible. The water surface is moderately rippled with a few small boats visible. The overall scene is bathed in soft sunlight.",
